ation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 实例方法</span>\n</code></pre>\n</div></div></div>', 'http://cdn.cssjs.club/images/16264179070001.jpg', '2021-07-06 11:06:22', '2021-07-16 06:45:08');
